column168: THE TRUCK AND TRAILER WAS SOUTH BOUND ON UTAH 87 AND THE DRIVER DRIFTED TO HIS RIGHT AND INTO THE SHALLOW BORROW PIT. WHEN HE CAME BACK ONTO THE ROAD THE TRAILER LAY OVER ON THE RIGHT HAND SIDE AND SUBSEQUENTLY CAUGHT FIRE AND BURNED BOTH UNITS DOWN. A PICK UP TRUCK DROVE INTO THE REAR AXLE OF THE TRAILER AND WAS CONSUMED KILLING THE DRIVER OF THE PICKUP TRUCK. THIS REPORT WAS DISCOVERED MISSING AND ENTERED ON 10/16/92.
